entries.femaleVariant: Hello, I was just on the line with Candice, but the call dropped.
OK, Nanda. Listen. I've been trying to file a complaint for an hour.
Yes, my adrenaline generator. Had it put in last week.
Well, it's not working. Not generating a damn molecule.
I reset... I reset it ten times. I just want to file a complaint, it is all under warranty
Wait, wait, wait. How's it not covered? What's not covered? A faulty implant?
So what if I take meds? What's depression got to do with your generator?!
No, no, this is an out-- Hello? Hello?!
Fuck. Yes, I'll wait! Yes, I'll press "one" to speak to an operator!
